This benchmark harness pulls third-party DSP libraries via CMake FetchContent
at build time. Those libraries retain their own licenses and copyrights:

  - Signalsmith Stretch (MIT)        https://github.com/Signalsmith-Audio/signalsmith-stretch
  - SoundTouch (LGPL)                https://www.surina.net/soundtouch/
  - Rubber Band (GPL / commercial)   https://breakfastquay.com/rubberband/
  - libsamplerate (BSD-2-Clause)     https://github.com/libsndfile/libsamplerate
  - r8brain-free-src (MIT)           https://github.com/avaneev/r8brain-free-src

See each upstream repository for its license text.
